{
  "texts": [
    "Artificial neural networks (ANN)Artificial Neural Network or Feed Forward Neural Net is the most common Neural Net type and has at least one hidden layer.",
    "The most advantageous feature of this type of neural net is that output computation is high-speed.",
    "However, training time with the backpropagation algorithm could be faster.",
    "Extreme Learning Machine is another type of ANN.",
    "The training algorithm is based on a generalized matrix inverse."
  ]
}